{\pard\plain\posx6068\posy3817\absw4757\absh0\dxfrtext0\dfrmtxtx0\dfrmtxty0\nosnaplinegrid{\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u66x\u114x\u105x\u110x\u100x\u97x\u114x \u112x\u114x\u111x\u116x\u101x\u99x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x \u97x \u108x\u97x \u99x\u108x\u97x\u115x\u101x \u116x\u114x\u97x\u98x\u97x\u106x\u97x\u100x\u111x\u114x\u97x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u113x\u117x\u101x \u100x\u101x\u115x\u97x\u114x\u114x\u111x\u108x\u108x\u97x \u101x\u115x\u112x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u111x\u115x \u100x\u101x \u111x\u114x\u103x\u97x\u110x\u105x\u122x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u108x\u97x\u98x\u111x\u114x\u97x\u108x\u44x \u99x\u111x\u109x\u111x \u117x\u110x\u97x \u109x\u101x\u100x\u105x\u100x\u97x \u103x\u97x\u114x\u97x\u110x\u116x\u101x \u100x\u101x \u108x\u97x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u112x\u114x\u111x\u116x\u101x\u99x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x \u97x \u108x\u97x\u115x \u116x\u114x\u97x\u98x\u97x\u106x\u97x\u100x\u111x\u114x\u97x\u115x \u121x \u97x\u108x \u100x\u101x\u114x\u101x\u99x\u104x\u111x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u100x\u101x \u111x\u114x\u103x\u97x\u110x\u105x\u122x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x\u46x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u68x\u101x\u115x\u97x\u114x\u114x\u111x\u108x\u108x\u97x\u114x \u116x\u97x\u108x\u108x\u101x\u114x\u101x\u115x \u100x\u101x \u102x\u111x\u114x\u109x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x \u121x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u99x\u97x\u112x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u116x\u97x\u99x\u105x\u243x\u110x \u101x\u110x \u101x\u108x \u116x\u101x\u109x\u97x \u100x\u101x \u100x\u101x\u114x\u101x\u99x\u104x\u111x\u115x}\par {\b0\i0\strike0\f7\cf0\fs21\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0 \u104x\u117x\u109x\u97x\u110x\u111x\u115x \u121x \u108x\u97x\u98x\u111x\u114x\u97x\u108x\u101x\u115x\u46x \u68x\u101x \u109x\u97x\u110x\u101x\u114x\u97x \u116x\u114x\u105x\u112x\u97x